50
00:03:32,671 --> 00:03:34,172
How are you so sure of the place?

51
00:03:35,340 --> 00:03:38,260
One of the victims
that Franco's soldiers buried,

52
00:03:38,343 --> 00:03:41,013
Manuel Blanco Trujillo,

53
00:03:41,096 --> 00:03:43,307
