and who was in it.

57
00:03:55,652 --> 00:03:56,738
My great-grandfather.

58
00:03:56,821 --> 00:03:58,614
He was a teacher and a photographer.

59
00:03:59,072 --> 00:04:01,033
By chance, before the war,

60
00:04:01,325 --> 00:04:03,660
